items.name: Deamon-Drug
items.description:
Temporarily increases the Damage of your Dinos by 20%.
Due to its toxicity Dinos will be weakened and take more Damage!
The Effect lasts for 6 Minutes!

items.name: Mega Deamon-Drug
items.description:
Temporarily increases the Damage of your Dinos by 50%.
Due to its toxicity Dinos will be weakened and take more Damage!
The Effect lasts for 3 Minutes!

items.name: Hardskin-Drug
items.description:
Temporarily reduces the Damage dealt and taken of your Dinos by 20%.
Due to its toxicity Dinos will be 25% slower!
The Effect lasts for 6 Minutes!

items.name: Phoenix Creation Detergent
items.description:
It will raise from the Ashes, from the ashes of an Argentavis, to be precise. This Detergent will create a Phoenix in your Argentavis guts and kill it from inside. While it may sound horible this seems to be the only process of creating this magical creature! Cannot be used while riding!
Your Argentavis needs to be atleast Level 240 to use this!

items.name: Reaper-luring-pheromone
items.description: Trough genetic engineering this pheromone can be used to Lure a Reaper Queen. Warning when consuming the Reaper Queen appears almost instantly use it far away from your base and be prepared!!! This puts your Body into huge stress, which will cost you 100 HP over 5 seconds. Cannot be used while riding!

items.name: Speed Increasing Drug (Wyverns & Griffins)
items.description:
Temporarily increases the movementspeed of your Dinos by 50%.
Due to its toxicity and smell most Dinos refuse to eat it.
Wyverns and Griffins seem to be able to consume it.
The Effect lasts for 2 hours!

items.name: Speed-Drug
items.description:
Temporarily increases the movementspeed of your Dinos by 20%.
Due to its toxicity Dinos will be weakened and take more Damage!
The Effect lasts for 60 Minutes!

items.name: Wake Up Potion (Parasympatomimeticum)
items.description: Stimulates the Parasympaticus which increases a Dinos Metobolism and wakes it up quickly. As a side effect the dino will recieve 3x the normal damage for the next 10 minutes. Use carefully.
